§0         Dear Jenny,§0
§0    Hope you have a§0
§0  great christmas and§0
§0   a happy new year!
#- §2ooooooooooooooooooo§0Decided to give you some "shineys" as you call them :P. Hopefully you can use them to beautify a build or something!§0
§0
§0Also have a cat egg and xp to name it, hopefully this one won't go suicidal on you! :P§0
§cooooooooooooooooooo
#- §2ooooooooooooooooooo§0 §0I've also added some festive fireworks to brighten up the night skies of Thaegon! There are some colorful New Years ones and some Christmas ones. Hope you enjoy them! :)§0
§0
§0
§0
§coooooooooooooooooo
#- §2o§co§2o§0Personal Note§co§2o§co§0
§0Jenny! I don't know how I got so lucky to meet someone as amazing as you, but I'm so glad I did. Looking back, it was so random a thing, you messaging me on Devoted, literally minutes after being mugged and pearled,
#- so I was feeling pretty bummed. I don't know what made you message me, but I'm very glad you did. You are an amazing person, and a great friend to talk to and be around. You never fail to brighten my day, no matter what. §0
§0
§0It means a lot to me to be
#- able to have that in my life. A thousand thank you's wouldn't be enough.§0
§0
§0Anyways, I hope you have a fantastic year in 2016, and I'm sure you will! :) I hope that I can be a part of it, even if it's just minecraft. §0
§0Happy Holidays!§0
§4<3§2 mummy
#- 